<br />Pay for credit cards?? Are you talking about the yearly fee, or interest on the credit? If you don't want a credit card, get a debit card. They work equally well for online payments, and the fee is like $10/year (at least in my bank).
<br />
<br />Besides, PayPal now allows you to transfer funds directly from a bank account to your PayPal account.

		

